Now, what can you tell me...

988
01:13:44,618 --> 01:13:46,984
是有關於這名字"艾莉"的?
about the name "Ellie"?

989
01:13:49,456 --> 01:13:51,253
艾莉
Ellie.

990
01:13:51,358 --> 01:13:54,122
是你認識的女孩? 你愛過的女孩?
Is that a girl you knew,
a girl you were in love with?

991
01:13:54,228 --> 01:13:56,423
