1000
01:14:27,127 --> 01:14:29,152
給我看你的臉, 大衛
Show me your face, David.

1001
01:14:31,098 --> 01:14:33,999
幫我開啟那道門
Help me open the door.

1002
01:14:43,544 --> 01:14:47,503
你的確是出了車禍, 你的確被毀容了
It's true you had an accident.
It's true you were disfigured.

1003
01:14:47,614 --> 01:14:50,048
