But not anymore.

1004
01:14:50,150 --> 01:14:52,050
記得嗎?
Do you remember?

1005
01:14:54,121 --> 01:14:56,021
他們的確修復了你的臉
They did fix your face.

1006
01:14:58,559 --> 01:15:01,357
把面具摘掉, 大衛
Take off that mask, David.

1007
01:15:01,461 --> 01:15:03,895
你會看到下面那張完美的臉
You'll see your face
