技術員!
Tech support!

1478
01:54:56,663 --> 01:54:58,096
大衛.埃姆斯
David Aames.

1479
01:54:59,432 --> 01:55:01,832
我想是時候正式的自我介紹了
I think it's time we had
a proper reintroduction.

1480
01:55:01,935 --> 01:55:05,098
我是艾德蒙.文圖拉, 來自綠洲計畫
I'm Edmund Ventura
from the Oasis Project.

1481
01:55:05,205 --> 01:55:07,537
原名生命延續, LE
Formerly Life Extension, LE.

1482
01:55:07,641 --> 01:55:09,666
- 技術員
- 是的
- Tech support.
- Yes.

1483
01:55:09,776 --> 01:55:11,676
是的, 我是你的技術支援...
Yes, I'm your tech support...

1484
01:55:11,778 --> 01:55:15,179
我們第一次見面是在150年前
and we first met
150 years ago.

1485
01:55:15,282 --> 01:55:17,614
哇, 靠
Oh, shit.

1486
01:55:17,717 --> 01:55:19,810
你向我推銷清晰夢境
You sold me the Lucid Dream.

1487
01:55:21,955 --> 01:55:23,684
他媽的發生了什麼事?
What the hell happened?

1488
01:55:23,790 --> 01:55:26,122
我試圖在酒吧裡警告你
I tried to warn you in the bar.

1489
01:55:26,226 --> 01:55:30,356
我告訴你必須運用控制, 一切取決於你的意志
I told you you must exercise control,
that it all depended on your mind.

1490
01:55:31,031 --> 01:55:32,521
所有這些...
All of this...

1491
01:55:32,632 --> 01:55:34,827
都是你的想像創造出來的
everything is your creation.

1492
01:55:34,935 --> 01:55:37,836
現在我們將迎來你抉擇的時刻
And now we're heading toward
your true moment of choice.

1493
01:55:38,872 --> 01:55:40,567
抉擇的時刻?
True moment of choice?

1494
01:55:40,674 --> 01:55:41,732
是的
Yes.

1495
01:55:46,913 --> 01:55:48,904
我什麼時候開始清晰夢境的?
When did the Lucid Dream begin?

1496
01:55:49,015 --> 01:55:50,915
記得夜總會那天嗎?
Remember the day
of the nightclub?

1497
01:55:51,017 --> 01:55:52,382
我們很快會再見的
We'll meet up soon.

1498
01:55:54,254 --> 01:55:57,781
那晚, 索菲亞離開後你睡倒在路邊...
That night, after Sofia left you and
you fell asleep on the pavement...

1499
01:55:57,891 --> 01:56:01,156
就是那個時刻, 你選擇作為拼接
that was the moment
that you chose for the splice.

1500
01:56:01,261 --> 01:56:04,059
- 拼接?
- 拼接
- Splice?
- Splice.

1501
01:56:04,164 --> 01:56:07,759
記憶中真實生活的結束, 清晰夢境的開始
The end of your real life and
the beginning of LE's Lucid Dream.

1502
01:56:07,867 --> 01:56:10,768
對接過去了很多很多年...
A splice of many, many years
which passed...

1503
01:56:10,870 --> 01:56:13,202
期間你都是在冰凍和夢中
while you were frozen
and dreaming.

1504
01:56:13,306 --> 01:56:15,536
那個時刻你從街上醒來...
From the moment
you woke up on that street...

1505
01:56:15,642 --> 01:56:17,837
就沒有任何傳統觀念上的真實了
nothing was real
in the traditional sense.

1506
01:56:17,944 --> 01:56:19,377
睜開你的眼睛
Open your eyes.

1507
01:56:19,479 --> 01:56:22,380
你的清晰夢境一直被"生命延續"監控...
Your Lucid Dream
is monitored by Life Extension...

1508
01:56:22,482 --> 01:56:25,679
一個專家小組在跟蹤你的每個想法...
and a panel of experts who are
following your every thought...

1509
01:56:25,785 --> 01:56:27,753
包括這個時刻
even at this moment.

1510
01:56:29,889 --> 01:56:31,914
抱歉, 搞得你很頭大
Forgive me.
I'm blowing your mind.

1511
01:56:35,962 --> 01:56:37,896
我可不喜歡這麼高
I'm not a big fan of heights.

1512
01:56:39,366 --> 01:56:40,856
我知道
I know.

1513
01:56:40,967 --> 01:56:43,765
我們從你記憶中消除了實際發生的事
We erased what really happened
from your memory.

1514
01:56:44,304 --> 01:56:46,772
- 消除?
- 是替換...
- Erased?
- Replaced.

1515
01:56:46,873 --> 01:56:48,431
...用一個更好的生活
By a better life...

1516
01:56:48,541 --> 01:56:50,202
在這個...
under these...

1517
01:56:50,310 --> 01:56:52,870
美麗的...莫內所鍾愛的天空下
beautiful, Monet-like skies.

1518
01:56:54,214 --> 01:56:55,613
我母親的最愛
My mother's favorite.

1519
01:56:56,549 --> 01:57:00,041
更好的生活...因為你擁有索菲亞
A better life
because you had Sofia.

1520
01:57:00,153 --> 01:57:04,185
你用年輕時的記憶構築著你的夢
You sculpted your Lucid Dream out
of the iconography of your youth.

1521
01:57:04,291 --> 01:57:07,551
比如一張曾讓你感動的唱片封面
An album cover
that once moved you.

1522
01:57:07,794 --> 01:57:08,886
唱片封面?
An album cover?

1523
01:57:08,995 --> 01:57:10,257
"有些事...
There are some things...

1524
01:57:10,363 --> 01:57:13,264
你還沒到年齡去瞭解"
that you're not old enough
to understand just yet.

1525
01:57:13,366 --> 01:57:17,632
一些電影向你展示了父親是怎樣的...
A movie you saw once that showed you
what a father could be like...

1526
01:57:28,248 --> 01:57:30,648
...或者愛是怎樣的
or what love could be like.

1527
01:57:30,750 --> 01:57:32,274
而某個女孩...
This was a kind woman...

1528
01:57:32,385 --> 01:57:35,115
特別的...
an individual...

1529
01:57:35,221 --> 01:57:37,451
...超過你的想像
more than your equal.

1530
01:57:37,557 --> 01:57:41,584
你只在現實中認識她, 但在夢中...
You barely knew her in real life,
but in your Lucid Dream...

1531
01:57:41,695 --> 01:57:43,595
...她是你的精神寄託
she was your savior.

1532
01:57:48,068 --> 01:57:51,196
現實中我怎麼了? 發生了些事
What happened in my real life?
Something happened.

1533
01:57:51,304 --> 01:57:52,703
你消除了什麼?
What did you erase?

1534
01:57:52,806 --> 01:57:54,398
你真想知道?
Do you really want to know?

1535
01:57:56,876 --> 01:57:58,434
把一切告訴我
Tell me everything.

1536
01:57:59,646 --> 01:58:02,547
夜總會的第二天早晨, 你在街上醒來...
The morning after the nightclub,
you woke up on that street...

1537
01:58:02,649 --> 01:58:04,446
一個人還帶著宿醉
hung over and alone.

1538
01:58:04,551 --> 01:58:06,178
你站起來, 然後離開
You got up, walked away.

1539
01:58:07,420 --> 01:58:09,980
你再也沒見過索菲亞
You never saw Sofia again.

1540
01:58:16,062 --> 01:58:18,053
我沒殺索菲亞
I didn't kill Sofia.

1541
01:58:19,742 --> 01:58:21,110
沒有
No.

1542
01:58:21,568 --> 01:58:25,066
你為了控制公司與董事會對抗
You battled your board
for control of the company...

1543
01:58:26,606 --> 01:58:29,473
最後是湯瑪斯.提普, 你父親的朋友...
and in the end it was Thomas Tipp,
your father's friend...

1544
01:58:29,576 --> 01:58:31,305
...你保住他工作的那個人...
the man whose job you saved...

1545
01:58:31,411 --> 01:58:34,244
...讓公司回到你的控制
who wrenched the company
back into your control.

1546
01:58:35,348 --> 01:58:36,747
湯米
Tommy.

1547
01:58:38,318 --> 01:58:39,717
可是後來...
But then...

1548
01:58:40,954 --> 01:58:43,582
有人...死了
somebody died.

1549
01:58:45,859 --> 01:58:48,327
你思念索菲亞
You longed for Sofia.

1550
01:58:48,428 --> 01:58:50,589
與世隔絕數月
You shut yourself away for months.

1551
01:58:50,697 --> 01:58:52,255
你感到孤獨
You were alone.

1552
01:58:52,365 --> 01:58:55,926
你再也忍受不了頭痛的痛苦
You couldn't stand
the pain anymore, the headaches.

1553
01:58:56,035 --> 01:58:57,559
你幾乎崩潰
You could barely function.

1554
01:58:58,605 --> 01:59:00,766
我在網路上找到你
I found you on the Internet.

1555
01:59:04,611 --> 01:59:07,205
我和你簽了份合同然後...
I signed a contract with you,
and then-

1556
01:59:28,635 --> 01:59:30,034
我記得了
I remember.

1557
01:59:39,712 --> 01:59:41,612
有人死了
Somebody died.

1558
01:59:43,349 --> 01:59:44,873
那就是我
It was me.

1559
01:59:52,058 --> 01:59:55,221
十二月晚些時候...
And on a day in late December...

1560
01:59:55,328 --> 01:59:57,319
你把自己交給我們
you gave yourself to us.

1561
01:59:59,866 --> 02:00:02,334
你進入了休眠的狀態
You're now in a suspended state.

1562
02:00:06,539 --> 02:00:10,999
你的朋友布萊恩.謝比在你的舊屋子舉辦了三天紀念會
Your friend Brian Shelby threw a
three-day memorial in your old home.

1563
02:00:11,110 --> 02:00:13,010
他是個真正的朋友
He was a true friend.

1564
02:00:22,555 --> 02:00:24,614
大家都想念你, 大衛
You were missed, David.

1565
02:00:47,013 --> 02:00:50,573
索菲亞始終沒能從悲傷中恢復過來
It was Sofia
who never fully recovered.

1566
02:00:51,818 --> 02:00:54,719
她似乎是最瞭解你的人...
It was she who somehow
knew you best...

1567
02:00:55,822 --> 02:00:58,723
和你一樣, 她永遠也忘不了那個晚上...
and like you, she never
forgot that one night...

1568
02:00:58,825 --> 02:01:01,726
真愛幾乎就要出現
where true love seemed possible.

1569
02:01:10,470 --> 02:01:13,370
往往最重要的, 大衛...
Consequences, David.

1570
02:01:29,422 --> 02:01:32,322
...都是那些小事
It's the little things.

1571
02:01:35,762 --> 02:01:37,662
小事
The little things.

1572
02:01:39,198 --> 02:01:41,598
根本就沒什麼大事, 是吧?
There's nothing bigger,
is there?

1573
02:01:50,510 --> 02:01:53,911
你的潛意識的確造成了麻煩
Your subconscious
did create problems.

1574
02:01:55,348 --> 02:01:57,578
美夢變成了噩夢
Your dream
turned into a nightmare.

1575
02:01:58,751 --> 02:02:01,413
不過現在問題解決了
The glitch has been corrected.

1576
02:02:02,755 --> 02:02:05,383
所以我只要想像某個事物
So all I have to do
is imagine something.

1577
02:02:05,491 --> 02:02:07,391
比如, 如果我要...
Like, if I wanted...

1578
02:02:07,493 --> 02:02:09,484
麥凱布現在就回來
McCabe to come back right now-

1579
02:02:13,499 --> 02:02:15,296
聽著
Listen to me.

1580
02:02:15,401 --> 02:02:17,096
這些人很危險
These people are dangerous.

1581
02:02:18,371 --> 02:02:21,807
我們有麻煩了, 現在必須離開這屋頂
We're in trouble.
We need to get off this roof now.

1582
02:02:25,278 --> 02:02:27,178
現在我們暫停...
We're now on pause...

1583
02:02:27,280 --> 02:02:29,771
你將回到你的夢中
and you're about to return
to your Lucid Dream.

1584
02:02:29,882 --> 02:02:31,713
所有事都會更新...
With all the upgrades...

1585
02:02:31,818 --> 02:02:33,718
你不會記得所有這些...
you won't remember any of this...

1586
02:02:33,820 --> 02:02:36,584
也不會為這次技術支援付費
nor will you be charged
for technical support.

1587
02:02:36,689 --> 02:02:39,214
現在就是你抉擇的時刻
It's now your moment of choice.

1588
02:02:40,326 --> 02:02:43,818
你可以回到夢中過著美麗的生活...
You can return to your Lucid Dream
and live a beautiful life...

1589
02:02:43,930 --> 02:02:47,764
...和索菲亞或者你希望的任何人
with Sofia or whomever you wish...

1590
02:02:47,867 --> 02:02:51,166
或者你可以選擇這外面的世界
or you can choose
the world out there.

1591
02:02:53,272 --> 02:02:55,172
"外面的世界"
"The world out there."

1592
02:02:56,709 --> 02:02:58,609
你可以讓我回到...
And you can bring me back...

1593
02:02:58,711 --> 02:03:00,770
就像小狗班尼那樣?
just like Benny the dog?

1594
02:03:00,880 --> 02:03:01,938
是的
Yes.

1595
02:03:02,048 --> 02:03:05,415
就像小狗班尼那樣
Just like Benny the dog.

1596
02:03:06,386 --> 02:03:08,980
當然現在你的臉和身體都能被復原
Your face and body
can be fixed now, of course.

1597
02:03:10,056 --> 02:03:13,457
但現實事情會大不一樣
But things
are very different now...

1598
02:03:13,559 --> 02:03:15,789
你的財富不會一直持有
and your finances
won't last long.

1599
02:03:17,163 --> 02:03:20,394
觀察小組正等待你的決定
Your panel of observers
are waiting for you to choose.

1600
02:03:25,238 --> 02:03:27,138
這沒有任何保證...
There are no guarantees...

1601
02:03:27,240 --> 02:03:28,537
但記住...
but remember...

1602
02:03:28,641 --> 02:03:30,666
即使是在未來...
even in the future...

1603
02:03:30,777 --> 02:03:33,712
甜蜜也不會是甜蜜...
the sweet is never as sweet...

1604
02:03:33,813 --> 02:03:36,213
...如果沒嘗過心酸的話
without the sour.

1605
02:03:54,133 --> 02:03:55,657
我該怎麼醒過來?
How do I wake up?

1606
02:03:56,269 --> 02:03:58,169
這是你決定的
The decision is yours.

1607
02:04:03,109 --> 02:04:05,805
這個地方也是我選擇的, 不是嗎?
And I chose this scenario,
didn't I?

1608
02:04:07,346 --> 02:04:12,306
是的, 去面對你僅存的對高度的恐懼
Yes, to face your last
remaining fear of heights.

1609
02:04:12,418 --> 02:04:14,352
大衛, 別信他們
David, don't listen to him.

1610
02:04:14,454 --> 02:04:17,355
你說得對, 這都是七矮人, 這是個圈套
You were right. This is
the seven dwarfs. It's a setup!

1611
02:04:17,457 --> 02:04:19,891
你不能相信他
You can't trust him.

1612
02:04:19,992 --> 02:04:24,088
別為他感到不爽, 大衛, 這人是你創造出來的
Don't feel bad for him, David.
This winning man is your creation.

1613
02:04:24,197 --> 02:04:28,099
他本能的去爭取他的存在, 但他不是真的
It's in his nature to fight for
his existence, but he's not real.

1614
02:04:28,201 --> 02:04:29,600
我是真的
I'm real.

1615
02:04:32,472 --> 02:04:33,700
我是真的
I'm real.

1616
02:04:34,540 --> 02:04:36,531
我有兩個女兒...
I have two daughters...

1617
02:04:36,642 --> 02:04:38,166
你知道的
and you know that.

1618
02:04:39,278 --> 02:04:40,870
她們的名字是什麼?
What are their names?

1619
02:04:55,661 --> 02:04:57,060
我是真的
I'm real.

1620
02:05:02,268 --> 02:05:05,328
我只是家庭娛樂的犧牲品?
I'm mortality
as home entertainment?

1621
02:05:05,438 --> 02:05:07,338
這不可能是我的命運
This cannot be the future!

1622
02:05:09,809 --> 02:05:10,867
可能嗎?
Can it?

1623
02:05:12,979 --> 02:05:14,139
可能嗎?
Can it?

1624
02:05:42,775 --> 02:05:44,504
再見
Good-bye.

1625
02:05:47,547 --> 02:05:50,812
這是一場自我覺醒的偉大旅程
It's been a brilliant journey
of self-awakening.

1626
02:05:50,917 --> 02:05:54,284
現在你只需要問問自己
And now you've simply got to
ask yourself this-

1627
02:05:54,387 --> 02:05:56,981
幸福對你來說是什麼, 大衛?
What is happiness to you, David?

1628
02:06:03,930 --> 02:06:06,330
我想過真實的生活
I want to live a real life.

1629
02:06:07,500 --> 02:06:09,866
我不想再做夢
I don't want to dream any longer.

1630
02:06:10,937 --> 02:06:13,496
最後還有什麼願望嗎?
Any last wishes?

1631
02:06:15,608 --> 02:06:19,008
就讓他們知道我的想法吧
Let them out there
read my mind.

1632
02:06:19,779 --> 02:06:21,679
祝你好運, 大衛
I wish you well, David.

1633
02:07:01,988 --> 02:07:04,286
瞧瞧我們
Look at us.

1634
02:07:04,390 --> 02:07:06,290
我被冰凍, 你卻死了
I'm frozen, and you're dead.

1635
02:07:07,493 --> 02:07:09,017
而我愛你
And I love you.

1636
02:07:11,030 --> 02:07:12,429
這是個問題
It's a problem.

1637
02:07:16,369 --> 02:07:18,769
我上了那輛車後就失去了你
I lost you
when I got in that car.

1638
02:07:19,872 --> 02:07:21,396
對不起
I'm sorry.

1639
02:07:23,676 --> 02:07:26,668
你還記得曾經對我說過的嗎?
Do you remember
what you told me once?

1640
02:07:27,513 --> 02:07:29,674
每一分鐘...
That every passing minute...

1641
02:07:30,917 --> 02:07:33,818
都有可能會改變一切
is another chance
to turn it all around.

1642
02:07:39,258 --> 02:07:41,158
我會再找到你的
I'll find you again.

1643
02:07:57,877 --> 02:08:00,471
下輩子我會再遇見你...
I'll see you in another life...

1644
02:08:00,579 --> 02:08:02,809
當我們都是貓的時候
when we are both cats.

1645
02:09:14,987 --> 02:09:16,921
放輕鬆, 大衛
Relax, David.

1646
02:09:17,023 --> 02:09:18,320
睜開你的眼睛
Open your eyes.

1647
02:09:28,500 --> 02:09:36,500
追悼會上那首歌名是: 
Ladies And Gentlemen We Are Floating In Space
(我們漂浮在宇宙中)

